&lt;p&gt;Oxford Health NHS Foundation trust is seeking a GP to provide care to its patients within Didcot Community Hospital. Didcot Hospital offers in-patient rehabilitation beds for adult people ‘stepping down’ from medical care in an acute hospital, or ‘stepping up’ from the community, and occasionally provides palliative care. The GP would be providing medical care on the ward as part of a multi-disciplinary team and advice to MDT colleagues working in the community from time to time. This would be a fixed term contract until the end of March 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Jeanne Fay, Associate Medical Director, Email: Jeanne.fay@oxfordhealth.nhs.uk,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 07500072129&lt;/p&gt;
